    "description": "沉浸在被霓虹灯照亮的街道中，高速刺激和跃动的动作等待着你。掌握涡轮增压赛车的艺术，驾驶在一个被霓虹灯点燃的世界中，追逐胜利，伴随着令人兴奋的合成波音乐和令人上瘾的游戏玩法。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/67036cd70b6c41c017940d0ee608bc04.webp?t=1693230831\" width=616 height=40 /></span></h2>你渴望挑战速度极限，坚定地握紧方向盘，目光注视着地平线，准备征服前方的道路，尽快抵达路径的终点。<br><br>但这并不是一场普通的比赛。这是一个令人振奋的体验，策略与精准相遇。这不仅仅关乎原始速度；更是关于掌握控制和技巧的艺术。你的秘密武器是涡轮增压器，它急切地为每次精妙漂移充电，绕过潜伏在等待的险恶转弯。<br>这是一个平衡的游戏，要知道何时踩下油门，何时优雅地跟随赛道的曲线舞动。涡轮增压器是你的盟友，以爆炸性的加速度奖励你熟练的操作，将你推向难以想象的速度。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/dd77a86808488fd23c0b37a5ddc31d03.poster.avif?t=1693230831\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/dd77a86808488fd23c0b37a5ddc31d03.webm?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/dd77a86808488fd23c0b37a5ddc31d03.mp4?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/1551635898c990631bd0bd146bb246ba.webp?t=1693230831\" width=616 height=40 /></span></h2>超过25条赛道和5张地图以复古波浪主题和80年代未来愿景为基础，将带您穿越充满活力的城市和棕榈树环绕的高速公路上脉动的街道，直至进入无边宇宙中挑战重力的高速公路。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/5c89863305e1af063159a4154546e75c.poster.avif?t=1693230831\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/5c89863305e1af063159a4154546e75c.webm?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/5c89863305e1af063159a4154546e75c.mp4?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/4d0c5778ed7e5fff456f06aacbd31f53.webp?t=1693230831\" width=616 height=40 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/d5efc80bacb5faff0287a73561af82f4.poster.avif?t=1693230831\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/d5efc80bacb5faff0287a73561af82f4.webm?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/d5efc80bacb5faff0287a73561af82f4.mp4?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>通过完成挑战，您将赚取金钱和积分，解锁车辆的定制部件和升级。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/d08341944a8c5914973cc8c9553a7c70.webp?t=1693230831\" width=616 height=40 /></span></h2>准备好以惊人的速度与强大的竞争对手进行正面交锋，充分发挥您在漂移和涡轮方面无与伦比的技巧。夺取胜利，作为回报，您将获得终极奖励：首领车辆！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/035c8eba5b8a26c8df2cf8a58bf23070.poster.avif?t=1693230831\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/035c8eba5b8a26c8df2cf8a58bf23070.webm?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/035c8eba5b8a26c8df2cf8a58bf23070.mp4?t=1693230831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368880/extras/b953661b49c642fcb3a1722ae3a2c7fc.webp?t=1693230831\" width=616 height=40 /></span></h2>每个赛道和游戏模式都将有在线排行榜，展示全球排名以及您与朋友之间的排名。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Over 15 vehicles</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Customize and upgrade your vehicles</strong><br></li><li><strong>More than 25 tracks and 5 maps</strong><br></li><li><strong>Boss racing challenges</strong><br></li><li><strong>Over 25 different synthwave songs</strong><br></li><li><strong>Different game modes</strong><br></li><li><strong>Online Leaderboards</strong><br></li><li><strong>Achievements</strong></li></ul>",
